                <pre style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: monospace; margin: 0;"><code>Comserv/lib/Comserv/Model/DBSchemaManager.pm
(615 lines)
                </code></pre>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-50">
            <h3 style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--header-font); font-size: var(--font-size-large);">Integration Points</h3>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-color); font-family: var(--body-font);">
                <li><strong>Models</strong>: <a href="/Documentation/Models" target="_blank" style="color: var(--link-color);">DBEncy, DBForager</a></li>
                <li><strong>Catalyst</strong>: Used as a Model component</li>
                <li><strong>Logging</strong>: <a href="/Documentation/Logging" target="_blank" style="color: var(--link-color);">Comserv::Util::Logging</a></li>
